{% doc %}
  @prompt
    You are a senior Shopify theme developer (OS 2.0).
    Using the attached reference screenshot, create a horizontal USP / information bar section that visually and functionally matches the design exactly.
    
    Layout Requirements:
    
    Full-width horizontal bar
    
    Display 4 info items in one row on desktop
    
    Each item contains:
    
    An icon on the left
    
    Text content on the right
    
    All items vertically centered
    
    Equal spacing between items
    
    Content Structure (per item):
    
    Title text (bold)
    
    Subtitle text (smaller, lighter color)
    
    Example items:
    
    “Delivery All Over India” – “Get door step delivery all over India”
    
    “COD Available*” – “COD facility to be available at select pin codes”
    
    “Whatsapp Support” – “Available on 9209176799”
    
    “Secure payments” – “With our Payment Partners”
    
    Design Requirements:
    
    White background
    
    Thin bottom border or subtle divider
    
    Minimal, modern ecommerce style
    
    Icons should be:
    
    SVG or icon-font based
    
    Same size and color
    
    Text left-aligned next to icon
    
    Responsive:
    
    Stack into 2 rows on tablet
    
    Horizontal scroll or stacked layout on mobile
    
    Shopify Section Requirements:
    
    Use Liquid + JSON schema
    
    Section settings should allow:
    
    Enable/disable section
    
    Adjust spacing (padding top/bottom)
    
    Use repeatable blocks for info items
    
    Each block should allow:
    
    Icon (SVG picker or icon class)
    
    Title text
    
    Subtitle text
    
    Code Output Rules:
    
    Provide complete Shopify section code
    
    Include:
    
    HTML (Liquid)
    
    CSS inside {% style %} tags
    
    JSON schema
    
    Code must be copy-paste ready
    
    Follow Shopify OS 2.0 best practices
    
    No unnecessary JavaScript
    
    Match spacing, alignment, and proportions as closely as possible to the reference image., i will add icon in schema too so pleease check alls 4 would come horizantal 
